## Coding Standards
- Strict TypeScript, no `any` unless absolutely necessary
- Server Components by default, Client Components only when needed
- Elevated but accessible voice — mythic but practical
- Every feature should feel magical, not mundane
- Comment the "Why", not just the "How"

